  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500780/extras/7cc7334f607c849cafd375c3447ee027.avif?t=1708410358\" width=460 height=214 /></span><br><br>Waifu Club is a <strong>very addicting puzzle game</strong> in which you must solve puzzles of the lovey <strong>Azumi</strong>.<br>Every awesome puzzle has 40 tiles.<br><br>The game has an <strong>amazing soundtrack</strong>, 8 levels of the beautiful Azumi in <strong>HD Quality</strong>.<br>This said the game is a <strong>perfect way to relax </strong> from a hard day at work.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>8 levels of our beautiful girl Azumi<br></li><li>Relaxing music and gameplay<br></li><li>all images in high HD quality <br></li><li>makes you forgot all your sorrows</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Puzzle Mode<br></li><li>Gallery Mode</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500780/extras/7cc7334f607c849cafd375c3447ee027.avif?t=1708410358\" width=460 height=214 /></span><br><br>Waifu Club is a <strong>very addicting puzzle game</strong> in which you must solve puzzles of the lovey <strong>Azumi</strong>.<br>Every awesome puzzle has 40 tiles.<br><br>The game has an <strong>amazing soundtrack</strong>, 8 levels of the beautiful Azumi in <strong>HD Quality</strong>.<br>This said the game is a <strong>perfect way to relax </strong> from a hard day at work.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>8 levels of our beautiful girl Azumi<br></li><li>Relaxing music and gameplay<br></li><li>all images in high HD quality <br></li><li>makes you forgot all your sorrows</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Puzzle Mode<br></li><li>Gallery Mode</li></ul>",
